Question 1 The Z-parameter matrix of a two-port network relates the port voltages and port currents as follows: [latex]
\left[\begin{array}{l}
\mathrm{V}_{1} \\
\mathrm{~V}_{2}
\end{array}\right]=\mathrm{Z}\left[\begin{array}{l}
\mathrm{I}_{1} \\
\mathrm{I}_{2}
\end{array}\right]
[/latex] The Z-parameter matrix (with each entry in ohms) of the network shown below is __________.

solution:
